@273  = ~(Ajantis was your lover on the Sword Coast, but your engagement broke before you parted there.)~
@274  = ~(Ajantis was your travel companion, nothing more.)~
@275  = ~(The portal takes you to another place...)~
@276  = ~Be prepared.~

